  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Dr. Mario was remastered for the Super Famicom and released as a stand-alone Nintendo Power service release, only in Japan, and also for the Nintendo Gateway System. The game also received a Satellaview broadcast.\n\nThe same version was previously bundled with Tetris and released in the West as Tetris & Dr. Mario.",
